==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Jub
<hw>Ju`b⟦eacute⟧"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<fld>(Arch.)</fld> <fld>(a)</fld> <def>A chancel screen or rood
screen.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The gallery above such a screen, from
which certain parts of the service were formerly read.</def> See
<cref>Rood loft</cref>, under <er>Rood</er>.⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

